================================================================================
PREAMBLE
================================================================================

This software consists of two distinct components with different licensing terms:

1. BASE MCP SERVER (Anthropic, PBC): The foundational Model Context Protocol server
   implementation, originally created by Anthropic, PBC.

2. ENHANCED ML/AI FEATURES (Kai Wyborny / PrismAero): Advanced features including:
   - TensorFlow.js-based semantic similarity engine
   - Universal Sentence Encoder integration for embeddings
   - Vector database with cosine similarity search
   - Adaptive model training and project-specific ML models
   - Project analysis with interface mapping and file monitoring
   - Context engine and intelligent relationship prediction
   - Background processing for automated analysis
   - All machine learning algorithms, training methods, and optimization techniques

